Task 1
Title: Utilize Bing Copilot to Research Market Trends
● Bing Copilot is a free, powerful AI-chatbot developed by Microsoft based on Open AI’s GPT and
DALL-E engines.
● Zero-shot prompting is the technique of directly requesting information without prior context
for factual responses - like generating market trends.
● One-shot prompting is the technique of giving some contextual information for the AI to build
upon existing factual information for generating more specific results
